1
00:00:17,914 --> 00:00:19,832
A lot has changed when
you were unconscious.

2
00:00:22,085 --> 00:00:24,003
The campus security has doubled

3
00:00:25,588 --> 00:00:27,188
and all who were involved in hurting you

4
00:00:27,757 --> 00:00:28,800
are being punished.

5
00:00:30,093 --> 00:00:31,511
This is too much, Ace.

6
00:00:33,346 --> 00:00:35,139
Aren't you too greedy?

7
00:00:37,850 --> 00:00:38,935
You have everything!

8
00:00:40,395 --> 00:00:41,771
If you really love him

9
00:00:42,814 --> 00:00:44,274
stop hurting him.

10
00:00:46,067 --> 00:00:48,236
I can't fight anymore, Ace.

11
00:00:49,696 --> 00:00:51,030
You don't have to.

12
00:00:53,866 --> 00:00:55,577
I'll fight for you.

13
00:00:56,703 --> 00:00:57,829
I love you.

14
00:00:58,913 --> 00:01:00,206
More than myself

15
00:01:01,833 --> 00:01:03,334
and everything that I have.

16
00:01:07,171 --> 00:01:08,423
Never leave me hanging

17
00:01:09,549 --> 00:01:10,549
darling.

18
00:01:11,634 --> 00:01:14,012
Love has no place in this hell.

19
00:01:14,429 --> 00:01:16,306
Love is just a poison.

20
00:01:19,267 --> 00:01:20,435
Handle this.

21
00:01:27,357 --> 00:01:29,109
You're just making this hard for yourself.

22
00:01:30,069 --> 00:01:31,069
You know

23
00:01:31,696 --> 00:01:33,156
despite what Nicky said.

24
00:01:34,606 --> 00:01:35,815
I can believe

25
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,633
love could grow in this hell.

26
00:01:40,913 --> 00:01:41,956
It's a pity

27
00:01:42,832 --> 00:01:44,417
that you fell for the wrong person

28
00:01:45,303 --> 00:01:48,097
in the wrong circumstance
and at the wrong place.

29
00:01:52,091 --> 00:01:53,468
Are you sure it's wrong?

30
00:01:56,471 --> 00:01:58,389
I see right through you, Nazzer.

31
00:01:59,390 --> 00:02:01,684
I know you're familiar with this feeling.

32
00:02:02,602 --> 00:02:03,602
I don’t.

33
00:02:04,354 --> 00:02:06,356
I can't release you right now.

34
00:02:07,607 --> 00:02:09,108
What do you want from me?

35
00:02:10,485 --> 00:02:11,736
Just let me go!

36
00:02:12,236 --> 00:02:13,488
Not right now.

37
00:02:15,281 --> 00:02:16,824
But he's waiting for me.

38
00:02:17,367 --> 00:02:20,036
It's better for both of you
if you don't go to the party.

39
00:02:20,578 --> 00:02:23,164
Why are all of you
against our relationship?

40
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:25,041
I'm sorry, Zein.

41
00:02:26,876 --> 00:02:29,045
I never wanted to be a hindrance.

42
00:02:32,924 --> 00:02:35,593
But you were already against us
since the beginning.

43
00:02:37,512 --> 00:02:40,473
Do you know why you can't go to the party?

44
00:02:42,225 --> 00:02:45,770
Supremo is planning to reveal everything.

45
00:02:46,484 --> 00:02:50,363
He's going to scream his heart out
about your relationship

46
00:02:50,698 --> 00:02:53,409
to everyone.

47
00:02:54,195 --> 00:02:55,195
Everything!

48
00:02:55,196 --> 00:02:56,280
No.

49
00:02:57,089 --> 00:02:58,257
He won't do that.

50
00:02:58,282 --> 00:03:00,243
You think you already
know Supremo that well?

51
00:03:00,368 --> 00:03:01,368
Huh?

52
00:03:02,103 --> 00:03:04,856
He will do that for you.

53
00:03:08,084 --> 00:03:10,001
And do you know what happens to him

54
00:03:10,002 --> 00:03:11,337
after he does that?

55
00:03:12,158 --> 00:03:15,842
The minute he goes through with his plan

56
00:03:16,313 --> 00:03:18,899
everything he has worked for will crumble.

57
00:03:19,345 --> 00:03:20,722
Especially his reputation.

58
00:03:21,667 --> 00:03:23,794
They will depose him
and rid him of his power.

59
00:03:24,228 --> 00:03:26,822
They'll treat him like trash.

60
00:03:28,271 --> 00:03:31,357
Will you let him do that for you?

61
00:03:35,445 --> 00:03:37,155
Despite this war

62
00:03:37,447 --> 00:03:40,491
we still respect Supremo.

63
00:03:41,534 --> 00:03:43,703
Respect equals power.

64
00:03:45,145 --> 00:03:47,692
If he loses that power

65
00:03:47,717 --> 00:03:50,739
the balance he created among
the gangs will instantly fall.

66
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:55,544
I think you're familiar
with what comes next?

67
00:03:56,048 --> 00:03:57,800
Our enemy gets stronger.

68
00:03:58,645 --> 00:04:00,844
Supremo managed to
hold back the administration

69
00:04:00,845 --> 00:04:03,514
from taking full control of this school.

70
00:04:04,674 --> 00:04:07,343
He is our shield and without him

71
00:04:08,081 --> 00:04:10,041
we are nothing.

72
00:04:14,484 --> 00:04:17,153
If I stay away from Supremo...

73
00:04:18,488 --> 00:04:20,281
We'll be out of his way too.

74
00:04:26,704 --> 00:04:28,206
Then let me go.

75
00:04:33,669 --> 00:04:35,963
I'll trust you just this once, Zein.

76
00:04:47,683 --> 00:04:48,683
Zein

77
00:04:50,128 --> 00:04:52,838
you're the only one who can save Supremo

78
00:04:52,863 --> 00:04:54,990
and this university.

79
00:05:08,037 --> 00:05:09,121
Hold up.

80
00:05:09,330 --> 00:05:10,610
Where do you think you're going?

81
00:05:10,635 --> 00:05:12,053
Let her through.

82
00:05:30,742 --> 00:05:32,285
Will she do as she's told?

83
00:05:33,233 --> 00:05:34,401
I don't know.

84
00:05:34,771 --> 00:05:36,605
But whatever her decision may be

85
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:38,340
we need to be ready.

86
00:05:39,354 --> 00:05:41,114
If they push through
with their relationship

87
00:05:42,264 --> 00:05:44,182
I'll take care of Supremo myself.

88
00:05:51,622 --> 00:05:52,748
Where have you been?

89
00:05:55,543 --> 00:05:56,543
Where else?

90
00:05:57,211 --> 00:05:59,380
I was monitoring the DGW.

91
00:06:00,214 --> 00:06:02,174
They had a meeting
at the east wing earlier.

92
00:06:02,473 --> 00:06:03,474
That's not enough.

93
00:06:05,041 --> 00:06:06,709
Add more surveillance.

94
00:06:07,349 --> 00:06:08,976
Impose scout parties.

95
00:06:09,415 --> 00:06:11,292
We need eyes and ears on everyone.

96
00:06:11,827 --> 00:06:13,578
Why don't you let Matt handle that?

97
00:06:13,603 --> 00:06:15,396
This is your responsibility!

98
00:06:16,856 --> 00:06:18,493
Don't fail us again.

99
00:06:55,704 --> 00:06:56,704
Zein

100
00:06:57,939 --> 00:06:59,065
what happened?

101
00:07:01,796 --> 00:07:02,797
It's nothing.

102
00:07:05,726 --> 00:07:06,726
We can do this.

103
00:07:07,852 --> 00:07:09,353
Don't give up.

104
00:07:15,414 --> 00:07:17,204
Can we really handle all of this?

105
00:07:19,210 --> 00:07:20,586
But I'm dead serious.

106
00:07:21,592 --> 00:07:23,469
Nothing matters if you're not beside me.

107
00:07:24,090 --> 00:07:25,090
Darling

108
00:07:25,466 --> 00:07:28,094
I want to dance with
you in front of everyone.

109
00:07:28,510 --> 00:07:30,462
It's one of my biggest dreams.

110
00:07:32,595 --> 00:07:34,097
Make that dream come true.

111
00:07:37,353 --> 00:07:38,562
Can I handle this?

112
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:20,580
Zein!

113
00:09:21,177 --> 00:09:22,251
Where are you going?

114
00:09:22,374 --> 00:09:24,042
Please, let's just stay back in the dorms.

115
00:09:24,043 --> 00:09:24,585
Huh?

116
00:09:24,585 --> 00:09:25,458
Why?

117
00:09:25,483 --> 00:09:26,878
I need to be at the SSG office.

118
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:28,546
- I'll see you later.
- Let's go back, Zein.

119
00:09:28,725 --> 00:09:30,006
Mia, let's talk about it some other time.

120
00:09:30,007 --> 00:09:31,050
See you later, okay?

121
00:09:31,075 --> 00:09:32,075
Zein!

122
00:09:33,209 --> 00:09:35,346
Where do you think you're going, bitch?

123
00:09:41,393 --> 00:09:42,895
You look confused.

124
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:47,733
Everyone in this campus knows
about you and Supremo.

125
00:09:48,359 --> 00:09:51,529
And how he gave you an exemption
even if you disobeyed the rules.

126
00:09:52,238 --> 00:09:54,198
Such a slut.

127
00:09:54,907 --> 00:09:57,034
She must have seduced our Supremo.

128
00:09:57,743 --> 00:10:01,079
Are we going to let this newbie do that
after what she did to our Supremo?

129
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:01,872
Of course not!

130
00:10:01,872 --> 00:10:02,373
No!

131
00:10:02,374 --> 00:10:03,707
We won't allow it!

132
00:10:04,250 --> 00:10:05,250
Go ahead.

133
00:10:05,459 --> 00:10:06,836
Try me.

134
00:10:08,546 --> 00:10:10,422
Do you know the punishment you'll get

135
00:10:10,756 --> 00:10:12,049
if you hurt me?

136
00:10:13,425 --> 00:10:16,720
I’m the Queen of this University.

137
00:10:17,012 --> 00:10:21,308
He fourth highest in the H10.

138
00:10:22,852 --> 00:10:24,520
The SSG Secretary.

139
00:10:26,605 --> 00:10:28,274
What punishment do you want?

140
00:10:29,233 --> 00:10:30,209
No!

141
00:10:30,234 --> 00:10:31,443
Don't let her scare you.

142
00:10:32,595 --> 00:10:33,680
This is wrong.

143
00:10:33,763 --> 00:10:35,781
- We can't hurt her.
- What?

144
00:10:35,782 --> 00:10:37,323
I don't want to be punished.

145
00:10:37,324 --> 00:10:38,534
I'm sorry, Roxane.

146
00:10:40,161 --> 00:10:41,161
You.

147
00:10:46,709 --> 00:10:51,505
You will never be an
exemption to this rule!

148
00:10:52,673 --> 00:10:53,841
Samantha?

149
00:10:57,011 --> 00:10:58,011
Do you know

150
00:10:59,805 --> 00:11:01,557
that I'm so annoyed by you?

151
00:11:03,307 --> 00:11:07,353
I've been angry with you from the start.

152
00:11:08,063 --> 00:11:09,565
Because you’re insecure.

153
00:11:10,205 --> 00:11:12,434
That may be true.

154
00:11:13,986 --> 00:11:14,986
But...

155
00:11:15,743 --> 00:11:17,411
I'm angry

156
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:20,482
because I see her in you.

157
00:11:22,728 --> 00:11:25,231
The only person I accepted as a friend

158
00:11:25,841 --> 00:11:27,833
in this hellhole.

159
00:11:30,981 --> 00:11:32,347
A friend

160
00:11:33,422 --> 00:11:35,591
who abandoned me in this hell.

161
00:11:36,208 --> 00:11:37,276
That's not true.

162
00:11:37,301 --> 00:11:39,303
I thought she wouldn't leave me

163
00:11:40,419 --> 00:11:41,971
but I was wrong.

164
00:11:41,972 --> 00:11:42,972
That's not what happened.

165
00:11:43,516 --> 00:11:44,557
She was killed by-

166
00:11:44,558 --> 00:11:45,558
No!

167
00:11:46,352 --> 00:11:47,436
I don’t care!

168
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:50,564
She left me alone and I hate her!

169
00:11:50,973 --> 00:11:52,066
And I hate you!

170
00:11:52,775 --> 00:11:54,735
And I hate all of you!

171
00:13:31,415 --> 00:13:32,415
Zein!

172
00:13:39,632 --> 00:13:40,632
You came.

173
00:13:42,913 --> 00:13:44,373
You look so beautiful.

174
00:13:46,597 --> 00:13:47,931
I'm so glad you're here.

175
00:13:57,235 --> 00:13:59,529
Happy birthday, Supremo.

176
00:14:07,242 --> 00:14:10,120
Are you okay, Zein?

177
00:14:17,837 --> 00:14:20,506
I hope after this night ends

178
00:14:21,591 --> 00:14:23,343
you can still forgive me.

179
00:14:24,109 --> 00:14:25,527
I love you, Ace.

180
00:14:27,663 --> 00:14:30,082
I want everyone to hear my answer to that.

181
00:14:32,284 --> 00:14:35,329
I have never loved anyone
as intensely as this before.

182
00:14:36,706 --> 00:14:38,332
And I'm so glad to say.

183
00:14:40,076 --> 00:14:42,315
I love you, Zein.

184
00:14:44,046 --> 00:14:45,256
More than anyone.

185
00:15:28,225 --> 00:15:29,310
Darling?

186
00:15:37,308 --> 00:15:39,018
That made me want to kiss you…

187
00:15:39,661 --> 00:15:40,661
but.

188
00:15:41,874 --> 00:15:42,874
I feel like

189
00:15:44,038 --> 00:15:45,206
there's something wrong.

190
00:15:51,295 --> 00:15:52,672
Supremo.

191
00:15:53,570 --> 00:15:54,613
I love you

192
00:15:56,970 --> 00:15:58,495
but I think we should stop.

193
00:15:58,496 --> 00:15:59,496
Darling

194
00:15:59,778 --> 00:16:00,778
maybe

195
00:16:01,942 --> 00:16:04,110
maybe you want to eat first?

196
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:05,340
Or sit?

197
00:16:06,055 --> 00:16:07,848
This hurts too much, Supremo.

198
00:16:08,578 --> 00:16:09,913
I’m hurting too.

199
00:16:12,464 --> 00:16:13,591
The pain is unbearable

200
00:16:14,477 --> 00:16:15,477
but...

201
00:16:17,563 --> 00:16:19,148
I can endure anything for you.

202
00:16:19,482 --> 00:16:21,276
But I can't do it for you.

203
00:16:26,732 --> 00:16:29,109
I'm going to pretend that
I didn't hear you say that.

204
00:16:30,811 --> 00:16:32,437
Do you want me to repeat myself?

205
00:16:36,330 --> 00:16:39,583
I can't take this pain anymore, Ace.

206
00:16:40,581 --> 00:16:42,082
That you've caused.

207
00:16:45,125 --> 00:16:47,336
We can't be together, Supremo.

208
00:16:49,572 --> 00:16:51,115
Loving each other for that short span

209
00:16:52,361 --> 00:16:53,931
was enough.

210
00:16:55,912 --> 00:16:57,122
No, it's not enough.

211
00:16:58,540 --> 00:17:01,376
I want to love you openly.

212
00:17:03,359 --> 00:17:04,359
Darling

213
00:17:05,059 --> 00:17:06,518
why can’t you trust me?

214
00:17:08,422 --> 00:17:10,090
I trust you, Ace

215
00:17:10,713 --> 00:17:12,465
with my whole life

216
00:17:17,199 --> 00:17:18,534
but I’m giving up.

217
00:17:19,001 --> 00:17:21,438
I just can’t fight for this shit anymore.

218
00:17:22,733 --> 00:17:24,110
We've barely started.

219
00:17:24,753 --> 00:17:25,833
You're ending it like this?

220
00:17:29,779 --> 00:17:30,779
Darling…

221
00:17:31,048 --> 00:17:32,633
Stop calling me that!

222
00:17:39,103 --> 00:17:40,103
Zein.

223
00:17:41,648 --> 00:17:43,233
I’ll give you another chance.

224
00:17:44,859 --> 00:17:47,445
If you walk ten steps away from me

225
00:17:49,239 --> 00:17:50,615
without looking back

226
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,585
forget everything that happened between us.

227
00:17:56,871 --> 00:17:57,871
But

228
00:17:59,499 --> 00:18:00,708
if you look back

229
00:18:01,834 --> 00:18:03,336
before the tenth step

230
00:18:05,964 --> 00:18:06,965
you're mine.

231
00:18:17,517 --> 00:18:18,517
Don't you have class?

232
00:18:23,147 --> 00:18:24,147
Full name, please.

233
00:18:24,607 --> 00:18:25,607
Zein.

234
00:18:26,234 --> 00:18:27,277
Zein Shion.

235
00:18:47,072 --> 00:18:49,741
Cause you're the type of bitch
that's qualified to be my secretary.

236
00:18:50,388 --> 00:18:51,932
So you need to be treated immediately.

237
00:19:17,410 --> 00:19:18,536
Thank you for lunch.

238
00:19:19,329 --> 00:19:19,806
Zein.

239
00:19:19,831 --> 00:19:20,705
Are you

240
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:22,624
allergic to spinach?

241
00:19:22,796 --> 00:19:23,796
I can never

242
00:19:23,958 --> 00:19:25,084
waste your efforts.

243
00:19:25,335 --> 00:19:26,269
Even if

244
00:19:26,294 --> 00:19:28,171
my body refuses.

245
00:19:29,359 --> 00:19:30,359
Help!

246
00:19:30,822 --> 00:19:31,822
Please.

247
00:19:51,485 --> 00:19:53,321
I'll get a rag.

248
00:20:15,468 --> 00:20:17,303
Goodbye, Zein Shion.

249
00:20:32,110 --> 00:20:33,753
What do you think you're doing?

250
00:20:33,778 --> 00:20:34,778
Zein?

251
00:21:05,635 --> 00:21:07,262
It doesn't matter.

252
00:21:08,604 --> 00:21:09,981
Nothing else matters.

253
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:12,483
It doesn't matter where life takes us

254
00:21:14,777 --> 00:21:18,489
you'll be my everything.

255
00:21:20,658 --> 00:21:23,870
You'll always be my everything.

256
00:21:25,788 --> 00:21:28,499
I won't lose anything
as long as I have you.

257
00:21:42,023 --> 00:21:43,023
I

258
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:45,101
Ace Craige

259
00:21:47,435 --> 00:21:48,686
will be your shield

260
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:53,775
your bulletproof vest and your knight.

261
00:22:16,958 --> 00:22:19,127
I can't fight anymore, Ace.

262
00:22:20,559 --> 00:22:22,102
You don't have to.

263
00:22:24,772 --> 00:22:26,523
I'll fight for you.

264
00:22:39,237 --> 00:22:43,986
I can fight death for you.

265
00:22:46,163 --> 00:22:47,622
I love you.

266
00:22:48,685 --> 00:22:50,771
It will always be you.

267
00:22:52,182 --> 00:22:55,560
Thank you for everything, Supremo.

268
00:23:14,188 --> 00:23:15,188
Zein.

269
00:23:17,984 --> 00:23:20,027
I want you to be happy no matter what.

270
00:23:22,780 --> 00:23:24,509
Whatever your decision will be.

271
00:23:27,198 --> 00:23:28,517
I hope it makes you happy.

272
00:23:30,788 --> 00:23:32,331
So whatever you decide on

273
00:23:34,904 --> 00:23:35,947
don't be scared.

274
00:23:38,025 --> 00:23:39,025
I think

275
00:23:40,756 --> 00:23:42,466
this is really goodbye for us.

276
00:23:47,096 --> 00:23:48,096
I love you.

277
00:23:49,432 --> 00:23:50,432
Zein.

278
00:24:54,747 --> 00:24:57,875
I guess history does like to repeat itself.

279
00:24:59,543 --> 00:25:01,170
I warned you, Supremo.

280
00:25:01,754 --> 00:25:03,046
I called all of you here

281
00:25:03,047 --> 00:25:06,508
to announce that I'm removing Ace Craige

282
00:25:06,509 --> 00:25:08,386
from his position as Supremo.

283
00:25:09,637 --> 00:25:11,722
Isn't that a bit too much, Madam Violet?

284
00:25:12,056 --> 00:25:13,891
I agree with Ms. Katherine.

285
00:25:14,475 --> 00:25:18,019
Supremo Ace Craige has done
so much for the university

286
00:25:18,020 --> 00:25:20,438
for us to discard his position this easily.

287
00:25:20,439 --> 00:25:22,984
Can you please reconsider, Madam Violet?

288
00:25:24,902 --> 00:25:26,112
You know the rules!

289
00:25:27,154 --> 00:25:30,992
The SSG President shouldn’t be
involved with anyone.

290
00:25:31,367 --> 00:25:34,537
Emotions don't belong in this place.

291
00:25:34,996 --> 00:25:36,831
It will only be your weakness.

292
00:25:38,124 --> 00:25:39,708
We don't have enough evidence to prove

293
00:25:39,709 --> 00:25:42,585
that he has a relationship
with Secretary Shion.

294
00:25:42,586 --> 00:25:44,005
What if it's just rumors?

295
00:25:46,048 --> 00:25:47,049
Rumors?

296
00:25:48,259 --> 00:25:49,593
We're not blind!

297
00:25:50,344 --> 00:25:52,179
Ms. Kath and I are with them all the time.

298
00:25:53,014 --> 00:25:56,516
The way Supremo treated
Secretary Shion is nothing special.

299
00:25:56,517 --> 00:25:58,227
They're just doing their jobs.

300
00:25:58,853 --> 00:25:59,853
Okay.

301
00:26:00,187 --> 00:26:02,356
Let's settle this once and for all.

302
00:26:03,190 --> 00:26:06,944
Let's hear it straight from
the Secretary's mouth.

303
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:08,820
There's no need for that.

304
00:26:09,739 --> 00:26:11,156
From their gazes alone,

305
00:26:11,157 --> 00:26:14,035
I can already see that
there's something between them.

306
00:26:14,577 --> 00:26:16,057
You've already made your assumptions.

307
00:26:16,328 --> 00:26:17,579
So there's no point hiding-

308
00:26:17,580 --> 00:26:19,165
We're not in a relationship.

309
00:26:27,089 --> 00:26:29,249
Supremo and I have never
been involved with each other.

310
00:26:32,845 --> 00:26:34,638
There's nothing between us.

311
00:26:38,835 --> 00:26:40,837
We're not idiots, Zein.

312
00:26:41,395 --> 00:26:44,105
We've noticed that you're always together.

313
00:26:44,106 --> 00:26:46,025
Because I am his secretary!

314
00:26:46,984 --> 00:26:49,445
The secretary of this fucking hell!

315
00:26:56,077 --> 00:26:59,663
Then answer this question.

316
00:27:01,082 --> 00:27:04,168
Did you ever love Ace Craige?

317
00:27:13,344 --> 00:27:14,344
No.

318
00:27:17,598 --> 00:27:23,312
Isn't that adequate proof that
the rumors have no basis?

319
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:25,980
Fine!

320
00:27:27,233 --> 00:27:32,446
Still, Supremo Ace Craige
is suspended for a week!

321
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:32,089
You know what hurts the most?

322
00:28:36,552 --> 00:28:39,597
Being denied by the girl I want the most.

323
00:28:41,765 --> 00:28:42,766
Just leave me alone.

324
00:28:44,182 --> 00:28:46,226
I don't want to hear your voice.

325
00:28:46,854 --> 00:28:48,480
Am I that easy to let go of?

326
00:28:55,154 --> 00:28:56,154
Yes.

327
00:29:03,829 --> 00:29:05,164
What you said yesterday...

328
00:29:06,665 --> 00:29:07,665
was that true?

329
00:29:09,543 --> 00:29:10,878
Did you really love me?

330
00:29:15,090 --> 00:29:17,134
Who could endure loving you?

331
00:29:19,851 --> 00:29:21,788
You are a heartless man.

332
00:29:24,608 --> 00:29:27,553
How can you expect me to
love you, when you are a devil.

333
00:29:35,295 --> 00:29:37,039
So please stop bothering me, Ace.

334
00:29:37,821 --> 00:29:39,156
You're just making my head ache.

335
00:29:42,576 --> 00:29:43,576
Is that so?

336
00:29:46,997 --> 00:29:48,123
Can I have one more favor?

337
00:29:50,417 --> 00:29:51,417
Just one.

338
00:30:04,311 --> 00:30:05,521
I want you to fight.

339
00:30:07,408 --> 00:30:08,408
Not for me

340
00:30:10,351 --> 00:30:11,686
but for your friends.

341
00:30:12,179 --> 00:30:13,472
Most especially for yourself.

342
00:30:16,443 --> 00:30:17,443
Don’t worry.

343
00:30:20,239 --> 00:30:21,281
I'm still breathing

344
00:30:22,032 --> 00:30:23,534
and a promise is a promise.

345
00:30:27,042 --> 00:30:28,210
I'll always be your shield

346
00:30:29,774 --> 00:30:31,192
your bulletproof vest

347
00:30:32,766 --> 00:30:33,766
your knight.

348
00:30:36,389 --> 00:30:37,881
No matter what happens

349
00:30:41,077 --> 00:30:42,095
you'll always be

350
00:30:43,435 --> 00:30:44,478
my queen.

351
00:31:21,773 --> 00:31:23,025
I'll fight

352
00:31:24,136 --> 00:31:26,024
but not just for myself

353
00:31:27,501 --> 00:31:29,044
or for my friends...

354
00:31:30,457 --> 00:31:34,419
I’ll also shed every blood I have for you

355
00:31:35,069 --> 00:31:36,278
until I drown

356
00:31:37,024 --> 00:31:38,391
and die for you...

357
00:31:39,427 --> 00:31:40,470
my king.

358
00:32:06,110 --> 00:32:08,485
Supremo disappeared for a long time.

359
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:12,063
I know the students feel
uneasy without him around.

360
00:32:12,703 --> 00:32:13,871
From time to time.

361
00:32:14,543 --> 00:32:16,628
I can't help it but to look for him.

362
00:32:38,836 --> 00:32:40,629
It is better off this way.

363
00:32:42,468 --> 00:32:44,095
I didn’t know you are this strong.

364
00:32:47,553 --> 00:32:48,553
Thank you.

365
00:32:50,722 --> 00:32:52,433
Thank you for saving him.

366
00:32:55,269 --> 00:32:56,645
I just did what was right.

367
00:32:58,106 --> 00:33:00,859
Because of you Madam Violet's plan failed.

368
00:33:04,559 --> 00:33:06,102
What do you mean?

369
00:33:09,658 --> 00:33:13,063
She's been waiting for an
opening to get rid of Ace but

370
00:33:13,996 --> 00:33:19,876
she couldn't do it easily because
he's important to the students.

371
00:33:21,073 --> 00:33:22,407
So when you arrived.

372
00:33:24,256 --> 00:33:26,433
Madam Violet finally had an instrument

373
00:33:26,458 --> 00:33:29,688
to contend against the one person
she can't fight head on.

374
00:33:35,571 --> 00:33:36,571
What's her plan?

375
00:33:37,714 --> 00:33:39,341
To instate her son as the Supremo.

376
00:33:40,113 --> 00:33:41,823
Liam Rivera.

377
00:34:29,655 --> 00:34:31,282
Liam Rivera is.

378
00:34:31,307 --> 00:34:33,008
Madam Violet's son?

379
00:34:33,419 --> 00:34:35,563
She wants Liam to be the Supremo.

380
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:38,766
But he doesn't seem...

381
00:34:39,036 --> 00:34:40,036
bad.

382
00:34:41,288 --> 00:34:43,610
I need to get to the bottom of this.

383
00:34:58,977 --> 00:35:00,672
Qin Shi Huang

384
00:35:03,071 --> 00:35:06,328
secret elixir to eternal youth...

385
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:10,382
and immortality.

386
00:35:14,849 --> 00:35:16,851
What does this mean?

387
00:35:17,415 --> 00:35:19,855
Is this connected to the secret lab
hidden in Hell University?

388
00:35:52,233 --> 00:35:52,922
I'll go ahead.

389
00:35:52,947 --> 00:35:53,742
Bye.

390
00:35:59,395 --> 00:36:00,395
Ms. Shion.

391
00:36:02,044 --> 00:36:03,044
Sir?

392
00:36:06,019 --> 00:36:07,312
We're too late.

393
00:36:08,829 --> 00:36:10,456
What do you mean?

394
00:36:11,396 --> 00:36:13,106
They know about the formula.

395
00:36:14,366 --> 00:36:15,664
Sooner or later

396
00:36:16,595 --> 00:36:18,180
they'll be able to replicate it.

397
00:36:18,764 --> 00:36:20,284
We will be helpless when that happens.

398
00:36:21,683 --> 00:36:23,727
If they completed the formula

399
00:36:25,095 --> 00:36:26,722
we need to fight back.

400
00:36:27,637 --> 00:36:28,971
We can't let them win.

401
00:36:29,511 --> 00:36:30,511
Listen

402
00:36:30,995 --> 00:36:33,024
I want you to stop what you’re doing.

403
00:36:33,889 --> 00:36:34,973
But...

404
00:36:36,325 --> 00:36:37,618
I'm looking out for you, Zein.

405
00:36:38,369 --> 00:36:40,204
I don't want you to get
hurt because of me.

406
00:36:41,288 --> 00:36:42,414
So please

407
00:36:43,155 --> 00:36:44,155
stop it.

408
00:37:26,373 --> 00:37:27,374
Where did you get that?

409
00:37:48,228 --> 00:37:49,896
Who gave this to you?

410
00:37:53,442 --> 00:37:54,442
Why?

411
00:37:58,470 --> 00:38:01,140
Don't you recognize this symbol?

412
00:38:04,520 --> 00:38:06,063
Devil God Warrior?

413
00:38:07,155 --> 00:38:08,155
No.

414
00:38:08,638 --> 00:38:10,432
This is the symbol of Raze Silvenia.

415
00:38:11,208 --> 00:38:12,585
How do you know that?

416
00:38:14,254 --> 00:38:18,716
I shouldn't have kept this from you

417
00:38:18,826 --> 00:38:20,870
but I didn't want Vanessa to know.

418
00:38:21,673 --> 00:38:23,091
And if the word gets out

419
00:38:24,171 --> 00:38:25,213
I'll be dead meat.

420
00:38:25,507 --> 00:38:27,142
And I don't want you guys
to be collateral damage.

421
00:38:29,134 --> 00:38:30,134
Jerome

422
00:38:31,348 --> 00:38:32,808
what are you trying to say?

423
00:38:34,769 --> 00:38:35,979
I'm part of them...

424
00:38:36,776 --> 00:38:38,087
I'm a Devil God Warrior.

425
00:38:44,872 --> 00:38:47,541
Don't torture yourself by
jumping to conclusions, Zein.

426
00:38:48,238 --> 00:38:52,075
Your questions will be
answered soon.

427
00:38:53,644 --> 00:38:55,521
Our scouts picked up new information.

428
00:38:56,207 --> 00:38:58,001
The admin is cooking up something

429
00:38:58,410 --> 00:38:59,786
something really big.

430
00:39:00,717 --> 00:39:03,053
Who else knows about you
being a DGW?

431
00:39:05,972 --> 00:39:08,099
The boys know about it.

432
00:39:09,267 --> 00:39:10,267
Please Zein.

433
00:39:11,066 --> 00:39:12,818
I don't want Vanessa to find out.

434
00:39:14,034 --> 00:39:16,103
And they don't need to
know about this.

435
00:39:39,458 --> 00:39:40,959
Jerome at Matt...

436
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:45,501
joined the gangs to
save us from this hellhole.

437
00:40:21,232 --> 00:40:22,232
It's late.

438
00:40:50,313 --> 00:40:51,356
Thanks.

439
00:40:57,794 --> 00:40:58,836
You know

440
00:40:58,861 --> 00:41:00,195
I'm doing okay.

441
00:41:04,856 --> 00:41:06,462
Why did you laugh?

442
00:41:08,759 --> 00:41:10,427
You're not okay, Zein.

443
00:41:14,652 --> 00:41:17,697
You don't have to smile if you don't to.

444
00:41:34,072 --> 00:41:35,860
I know you're in pain.

445
00:41:39,293 --> 00:41:41,665
If only I can carry
all of that pain for you.

446
00:41:43,346 --> 00:41:44,889
I would have done it in a heartbeat.

447
00:41:56,322 --> 00:41:58,449
Why didn't you help me?

448
00:42:02,014 --> 00:42:03,735
I need to think of the balance.

449
00:42:04,784 --> 00:42:07,245
Ace needs to be our Supremo.

450
00:42:08,058 --> 00:42:12,145
And you make your own decisions, Zein.

451
00:42:14,228 --> 00:42:18,482
I don't want to be a hindrance
to any of your decisions.

452
00:42:45,275 --> 00:42:46,443
Follow your heart

453
00:42:47,136 --> 00:42:48,136
right?

454
00:42:56,463 --> 00:42:57,464
I'm sure Matt

455
00:42:58,337 --> 00:43:00,631
that you'll find the right girl for you.

456
00:43:04,825 --> 00:43:09,330
Why, do you know another
Zein Shion in this world?

457
00:43:12,135 --> 00:43:13,135
Huh, Zein?

458
00:43:15,805 --> 00:43:16,973
No.

459
00:43:19,642 --> 00:43:23,646
But someone better
than Zein Shion will come.

460
00:44:11,022 --> 00:44:12,398
Supremo isn't here yet?

461
00:44:15,073 --> 00:44:16,699
Isn't it obvious?

462
00:44:21,454 --> 00:44:22,997
Maybe he already left you?

463
00:44:28,214 --> 00:44:29,256
I'm kidding.

464
00:44:30,197 --> 00:44:31,197
Actually

465
00:44:31,537 --> 00:44:32,997
we met earlier.

466
00:44:35,904 --> 00:44:36,904
Okay.

467
00:44:43,866 --> 00:44:44,909
You're not going to class?

468
00:44:51,787 --> 00:44:52,871
Do I have to?

469
00:44:53,629 --> 00:44:54,797
I'm the Queen.

470
00:44:56,387 --> 00:44:59,015
And he’s the SSG President.

471
00:45:05,401 --> 00:45:08,237
The queen should be a model student...

472
00:45:09,059 --> 00:45:10,853
just like the SSG president.

473
00:46:37,632 --> 00:46:39,424
Ein! Zein! Hurry!

474
00:46:39,425 --> 00:46:40,425
Stand up!

475
00:46:40,510 --> 00:46:41,510
Zein!

476
00:46:41,552 --> 00:46:41,886
Hurry!

477
00:46:41,887 --> 00:46:42,929
What's wrong, Supremo?

478
00:46:44,097 --> 00:46:44,597
Faster!

479
00:46:44,598 --> 00:46:45,598
What's happening?

480
00:46:49,706 --> 00:46:50,706
Wait!

481
00:46:51,070 --> 00:46:52,070
Zein!

482
00:46:52,563 --> 00:46:53,555
No!

483
00:46:53,580 --> 00:46:54,580
Stop!

484
00:46:55,650 --> 00:46:56,650
Supremo!

485
00:46:56,651 --> 00:46:57,277
Zein!

486
00:46:57,277 --> 00:46:58,277
Supremo!

487
00:46:58,695 --> 00:46:59,904
Let me go!

488
00:47:00,363 --> 00:47:01,864
Let go of me!

489
00:47:03,741 --> 00:47:05,118
Supremo!

490
00:47:06,452 --> 00:47:07,537
Zein!

491
00:47:08,434 --> 00:47:09,434
No!

492
00:47:12,865 --> 00:47:14,841
Let me go!

493
00:47:15,223 --> 00:47:16,766
Supremo!

494
00:47:21,853 --> 00:47:22,853
Hoy.

495
00:47:28,182 --> 00:47:29,182
Hoy.

496
00:48:33,122 --> 00:48:34,122
Darling.

497
00:48:36,584 --> 00:48:37,584
Please come back.

498
00:48:38,503 --> 00:48:40,004
This is a message from Supremo.

499
00:48:41,047 --> 00:48:43,049
I haven't seen him all day.

500
00:48:47,136 --> 00:48:48,262
Maybe

501
00:48:48,471 --> 00:48:49,722
he has no plan to come back

502
00:48:49,972 --> 00:48:51,224
or...

503
00:48:51,766 --> 00:48:53,226
he's with someone else?

504
00:48:55,311 --> 00:48:57,063
You're so fragile

505
00:48:57,605 --> 00:48:59,482
and easy to break, Zein.

506
00:49:00,441 --> 00:49:02,318
Let that monster in you out.

507
00:49:02,610 --> 00:49:04,361
Any day now

508
00:49:04,570 --> 00:49:07,490
your suffering will end.

509
00:49:09,117 --> 00:49:10,117
Now

510
00:49:10,410 --> 00:49:12,370
all of you must rest.
